Definition: a diode vacuum tube in which the flow of electrons from a central cathode to a cylindrical anode is controlled by crossed magnetic and electric fields
Example: used mainly in microwave oscillators
Synonyms: tube, a, diode, vacuum, in, which, the, flow, of, electrons, from, central, cathode, to, cylindrical, anode, is, controlled, by, crossed, magnetic, and, electric, fields, used, mainly, microwave, oscillators
Category: noun.artifact
